newsitem.title: USA: Iowa-S Minn cattle market not well tested - USDA.
newsitem.headline: Iowa-S Minn cattle market not well tested - USDA.

text.p: Slaughter steers and heifers not well tested, compared with Monday's close, USDA said.
Trade slow. Demand light to moderate. Seller interest light. Offerings light.
Steers - Select to mostly Choice 2-4 1225 lbs ld 68.00 Heifers - Select to mostly Choice 2-4 1100-1200 lbs few 67.00-68.00.
